Task 1 - Top 5 Products by Sales in 2022

Objective
The objective of this task was to identify the top-performing products in the "Mobiles & Tablets" category based on sales quantity during the year 2022 using valid transaction records.

Tools Used
- Python
- Excel
- Matplotlib

Dataset Features Used
- category
- order_date
- is_valid
- sku_name
- qty_ordered

Analysis Performed
The dataset was filtered to include only the "Mobiles & Tablets" category for the year 2022 where valid orders were marked as 1. Product-wise sales quantities were aggregated and ranked in descending order to identify the top 5 highest-selling products.

Visualization
A horizontal bar chart was created using Matplotlib to visually compare the sales quantity of the top-performing products. The visualization helped highlight product demand and category performance clearly.

Key Insights
Lenovo Pad P12 emerged as the highest-selling product in the category, followed by Samsung Galaxy M14 5G and Vivo V29e. The analysis showed strong demand concentration among a few key mobile and tablet products during 2022.

